org.jnosql.diana.api.document

Interface DocumentCollectionManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, CloseResource

    public interface DocumentCollectionManager
extends CloseResource
    Interface used to interact with the persistence context to DocumentCollectionEntity The DocumentCollectionManager API is used to create and remove persistent DocumentCollectionEntity instances, to find entities by their primary key, and to query over entities.
